@startuml
title Activity Diagram: Document Tools (Scan & OCR)

start
:User selects "Scan Document";
:Open Device Camera;
:Capture Image;

:Detect Document Edges;
:Crop Image;

:Pass image to Google ML Kit (OCR);
if (Text Extracted Successfully?) then (Yes)
  :Display Extracted Text;
  :User can copy or edit text;
else (No)
  :Show "No text found" error;
endif

stop
@enduml
